      "value": "<p>Dwarves have a land speed of 20 feet, which is never modified when they are @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.conditions.Item.OwZA6flUQPH0jPA0]{Encumbered} or wearing heavy armor. They also gain a +2 species bonus to saving throws against @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.rules.JaRMioj4isNp7r1P.JournalEntryPage.ZaS9H4rwaFIQTUBC]{Poisons}, spells, and spell-like abilities, and when standing on the ground they gain a +4 species bonus to their KAC against bull rush and trip combat maneuvers.</p>\n<p><em>Toggle on/off KAC bonus against&nbsp;<span>bull rush and trip combat maneuvers in the Modifiers tab.</span></em></p>"
